# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets honors this file (same _headers feature as
# Pages). It's copied verbatim from web/ into build/web/ by `flutter build web`.
#
# The HTML document is served from a different origin (Django at /room/) and
# fetches these assets cross-origin via ASSET_BASE, so they must be CORS-enabled
# -- mirroring scripts/serve_web.py used for local testing. Not needed if you
# ever serve the assets from the same host as the page (see wrangler.toml).
/*
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin
